data.description: Double corner lot two-flat in hot Avondale location just a few blocks to Belmont subway! Expansive, fully landscaped back and side yards for the best outdoor living in the city you'll see. Greenhouse/potting shed/outdoor workshop that's loaded with charm and function. Meticulously clean, upgraded interior with many fun 50s finishes. Your retro buyers will love it. Big rooms, big bedrooms - fit king beds. Huge open floor plans. Unmatched south light. Second floor spirals up to finished attic for two extra rooms that could make a fantastic en-suite. Skylights and upper-floor south windows add to charm. Excellent airbnb potential - could generate substantial, additional income! Multiple decks, patios, grassy yard, indoor/outdoor bar, two garages. All with a white picket fence!
